<li>JavaScript DOM manipulation and event handling</li>
<li>Canvas API for graphics rendering</li>
<li>Web Audio API for sound synthesis</li>
<li>Feature detection for cross-browser compatibility</li>
<li>User experience principles and interaction design</li>
</ul>

