<h1 style="font-size: 20pt;">Chapter 8: Conclusion</h1>

<h2>8.1 Project Summary</h2>
<p>This educational website successfully showcases the rich cultural heritage of Omani castles through an interactive digital experience. Built using modern web technologies, the project demonstrates proficiency in multimedia integration, responsive design, and interactive functionality.</p>

<h2>8.2 Key Achievements</h2>
<ul>
<li>✅ Fully responsive design with mobile hamburger menu</li>
<li>✅ Interactive 3D Khanjar visualization with controls</li>
<li>✅ Image editor with 12 filter effects</li>
<li>✅ Web Audio API synthesized music</li>
<li>✅ Hidden Easter Egg feature</li>
<li>✅ YouTube video integration</li>
<li>✅ Cross-browser compatibility</li>
<li>✅ Professional project documentation</li>
</ul>

<h2>8.3 Areas for Improvement</h2>
