</ul>

<h2>8.4 Final Remarks</h2>
<p>This project represents the culmination of skills learned throughout the Digital Media course. The interactive nature of the website demonstrates a comprehensive understanding of multimedia integration, while the responsive design showcases proficiency in modern web development practices.</p>

<p>The combination of educational content about Omani heritage with technical implementation creates an engaging learning experience that meets all course requirements while providing value to visitors interested in learning about Omani architecture and culture.</p>

